org.apache.calcite.runtime

类 FlatLists.Flat4List<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.runtime.FlatLists.AbstractFlatList<T>
      • org.apache.calcite.runtime.FlatLists.Flat4List<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - Element type
    所有已实现的接口:
    Comparable<List>, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>, RandomAccess, FlatLists.ComparableList<T>
    封闭类:
    FlatLists

    protected static class FlatLists.Flat4List<T>
extends FlatLists.AbstractFlatList<T>
implements FlatLists.ComparableList<T>
    List that stores its four elements in the four members of the class. Unlike ArrayList or Arrays.asList(Object[]) there is no array, only one piece of memory allocated, therefore is very compact and cache and CPU efficient.

    The list is read-only, cannot be modified or re-sized. The elements may be null.

    The list is created via FlatLists.of(java.util.List).
